$ VB Editor: Tools -> Digital Signature

*Tools -> Digital Signature* allows to digitally sign a → development/languages/VBA[VBA]-macro project for
Excel, Word, Outlook, Visio, PowerPoint or Publisher.

sa:
  It's possible to create a self-signed → development/security/cryptography/Public-key-certificate[certificate] with the
  → Windows/dirs/Program-Files/Microsoft-Office/root/OfficeN/SELFCERT_EXE[`SELFCERT.EXE`] executable which comes with
  → Microsoft/Office and is installed under the → Windows/dirs/Program-Files/Microsoft-Office/root/OfficeN[Office installation root].

  → development/security/cryptography/Digital-signature
